er of its cultural production.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 06. Mrz 2024) 0aChristian saintszCyprusvBiography. 0aChristian saintszCyprus. 0aChurch historyyPrimitive and early church, ca. 30-600. 7aRELIGION / Ancient.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertUniversity of California Press Complete eBook-Package 2016z978311066754740uhttps://doi.org/10.1525/978052096498340uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780520964983423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780520964983/original  a978-3-11-066754-7  University of California Press Complete eBook-Package 2016b2016  aEBA_FAO  aEBA_UCA_YUP  aGBV-deGruyter-alles